'''Alter Damage''' was a [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|technique]] used by the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] to change the damage their [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] inflicted upon a target.

==Description==
Mastery of this skill came hand-in-hand with mastery over [[Lightsaber combat/Legends|lightsaber combat]], as it was used in conjunction with use of the weapon. When used correctly, a practitioner could manipulate the energy of the lightsaber and reduce the damage caused to the target. Used while fighting both living and non-living opponents, this technique could make the difference between killing an opponent or completely disabling a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] or piece of machinery.<ref name="FTGG" />

